OAS: Peru Should Suspend Spy Chief
</SUBHEAD>
<P>
   LIMA, Peru (AP) -- The Organization of American States demanded Saturday that
the government of President Alberto Fujimori suspend Peru's intelligence chief
and other officials allegedly involved in the bribing of an opposition
