(Saturday night EDT) that the expulsion of the Romanian lifting team was ordered
by the International Weightlifting Federation. Under federation rules, any
nation is suspended from competition for the rest of that year if three or more
of its weightlifters test positive for banned drugs. A third Romanian
weightlifter tested positive earlier this year.
</P>
