<HEADLINE> Predators 5, Thrashers 3  </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
   SOUTHAVEN, Miss. (AP) -- Greg Classen, Rob Valicevic and Ryan
Tobler scored second-period goals to give the Nashville Predators a
5-3 victory Saturday night over the Atlanta Thrashers in the
preseason opener for both teams.
</P>
<P>
